text: Heinrich Albert (German: Heinrich Albert) was a German classical guitarist, composer and bassist, born on July 16, 1870, in Würzburg, Germany, and died on March 12, 1950 in Gauting, Germany. ==References== Category:1870 births Category:1950 deaths Category:20th-century German composers Category:German musicians Category:People from Würzburg
title: Heinrich Albert (guitarist)
